Class ImmutableArrayDoubleList

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Double>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Double>, java.util.List<java.lang.Double>, DoubleCollection, PrimitiveCollection<java.lang.Double>, DoubleIterable, DoubleList, PrimitiveList<java.lang.Double>, PrimitiveCollectable<java.lang.Double>

    public final class ImmutableArrayDoubleList
extends AbstractDoubleList
    Immutable array-based implementation of DoubleList for primitive int elements.

    This class implements List allowing seamless integration with other APIs.

    Add, Remove, Set and Clear are not supported as this class is immutable.

    Since:
    1.0
